constraints.ocl:
context Store
inv: self.coupons->size() >= 1 and self.coupons->size() <= 1

context Store
inv: self.products->size() >= 2 and self.products->size() <= 3

context Cart
inv: self.items->notEmpty() implies self.items->sortedBy(x | x.quantity)->first().quantity <= self.items->sortedBy(x | x.quantity)->last().quantity

context Address
inv: self.country <> null and self.postalCode <> null

context CartItem
inv: self.quantity >= 23 and self.quantity <= 75

context Customer
inv: not(self.customerId <> null and self.email <> null)

context DiscountRule
inv: self.percentOff <> null and self.minOrderTotal <> null

context Cart
inv: self.createdAt.size() >= 5 implies self.createdAt.substring(1, 5) = 'value'

context OrderItem
inv: self.unitPrice >= 8 and self.unitPrice <= 27

context Product
inv: self.variants->forAll(x, y | x <> y implies x.priceDelta <> y.priceDelta)

context Order
inv: self.items->forAll(x, y | x <> y implies x.unitPrice <> y.unitPrice)

context Product
inv: self.variants->notEmpty() implies self.variants->last().variantId <> null

context Coupon
inv: self.code <> '' and self.code.size() > 0

context Cart
inv: self.items->notEmpty() implies self.items->last().quantity <> null

context Address
inv: not(self.country.size() >= 10 implies self.country.substring(1, 10) = 'value')

context Coupon
inv: not(self.validUntil <> null implies self.code <> null)

context Store
inv: (self.coupons->size() >= 2 and self.coupons->size() <= 2) and (self.coupons->size() < 2)

context Address
inv: not((self.country <> null) = (self.postalCode <> null))
